Dismiss a dialog

Usage: bl dialog dismiss [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl dialog dismiss
  # Dismiss/cancel a dialog
